title: Mulatto, Big Bank, DJ Scream, King Unk - Fail To Plan, Plan To Fail
itunes:title: Mulatto, Big Bank, DJ Scream, King Unk - Fail To Plan, Plan To Fail
description:
Mulatto joins BIG FACTS to discuss her name, ATL female rap scene, the remix to her new single B-- From Da SOUF with Trina & Saweetie.

King Unk makes an appearance as well for some OG talk with BIG BANK and DJ SCREAM.
